{"id":"11038","name":"TrippleTap Reminders","tagline":"Create a reminder with URL and last image taken.","icon":"ios15 c2071128575 g59722","latest":"31762","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><img alt=\"TrippleTap Reminder\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43663476/153335868-460caecf-a013-41e2-a448-862171dbb086.png\"></p>\n<p>This shortcut creates a reminder on a list set at install at a time in the future specified at install including a timestamp in <a href=\"https://github.com/extratone/bilge/wiki/DavodTime\">DavodTime</a>, a URL captured from the clipboard, and the last image saved. I have it set to be triggered on the Triple tap <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT211781\">Back Tap</a> setting.</p>\n<h3>Steps</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>An <a href=\"https://www.matthewcassinelli.com/actions/ask-for-input/\">Ask For Input</a> action prompts for the reminder title.</li>\n<li>A duration of your choosing is added to the current time with an <a href=\"https://www.matthewcassinelli.com/actions/adjust-date/\">Adjust Date</a> action.</li>\n<li>A <a href=\"https://www.matthewcassinelli.com/actions/get-latest-photos\">Get Latest Photos</a> action gets the latest photo saved.</li>\n<li>A URL - if any - is grabbed from the clipboard.</li>\n<li>A reminder is created using an <a href=\"https://www.matthewcassinelli.com/actions/add-new-reminder\">Add New Reminder</a> action with the details gathered above.</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2>Contact</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://davidblue.wtf/db.vcf\">Contact Card</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://t.me/extratone\">Telegram</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"mailto:davidblue@extratone.com\">Email</a> </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/NeoYokel\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@DavidBlue\">Mastodon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://discord.gg/0b9KQUKP858b0iZF\">Discord</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://raindrop.io/davidblue/social-directory-21059174\">-Everywhere-</a>...</li>\n</ul>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><str